{
  "texts": [
    "Here by Hom we mean HomC.",
    "For notational simplicity, we will often drop the subscript on Hom when there is no confusion from the context.",
    "By choosing a (conventional) gauge for the F-symbols (see e.g.",
    "[12]), we have θ 2 ijk = ⟨Li⟩⟨Lj⟩⟨L k ⟩.",
    "It coincides with the g-function for general conformal interfaces among 2d CFTs and is positive by unitarity (in fact bounded from below by 1)."
  ]
}